bioData: Chef Michael Smith is a is a Japanese chef who has a unique style of blending Japanese cuisine with Western ingredients. He is best known for his appearance on the Japanese television show Iron Chef.

Emily Johnson is a talented chef with 8 years of experience in creating flavorful and aromatic dishes. He specializes in using fresh vegetables and herbs to create healthy and nutritious meals for his clients
